0th.270: Well drillers let the water run to clear a well they just drilled for a rancher that leases land from the Rosebud Sioux Reservation. The power lines in the background are a relic from when the power companies were implicit with pumping out the aquifer - they would run lines for miles to your pump for free. But now there are just too many wells for the power companies to afford this - so there are more diesel and solar pumps being put in now.
